## Week 12 Update

### What I Did This Week

This week I moved from data wrangling into exploratory analysis and visualization. Using the merged dataset I built in Week 11, I calculated my two affordability metrics across the full 1984 to 2024 period and created interactive visualizations using Plotly to explore how each has changed over time.

The interactive chart below has three panels that all share the same x-axis. Hover over any point to see exact values, zoom into specific time periods, and pan across the full timeline. The gray shaded areas mark the 2008 financial crisis and the COVID recession.

